#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
AI IoT Air Quality Monitor - Linux side for Arduino UNO Q.

This runtime intentionally avoids RouterBridge and App Lab. It reads JSON Lines
from the MCU through a normal serial port, computes CO2 and lightweight AI
signals, persists state, queues failed HTTP payloads in SQLite, and keeps running
through bad serial lines, sensor gaps, and server/network failures.
"""

